Cell["\<\
Indeed, it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s a well known fact that half-wave layers have no \
effect on reflectance or transmittance of assemblies, at wavelengths at which \
they are truly half-wave.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7294395930148087`*^9, 3.7294395945810685`*^9}, {
   3.7294396264058104`*^9, 3.72943974926853*^9}, {3.72944018304515*^9, 
