Cell["\<\
Of course, this assumes a particular value of the refractive index. According \
to Goldsmith Table 5.1, fused silica is 1.812 \[PlusMinus] 0.003 at 94.3 GHz, \
but 1.949 at 105.3 GHz. Whatever the material used, its refractive index \
better be known precisely to determine the exact optical thickness of the \
window:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.730553343488653*^9, 3.7305534376772976`*^9}, {
  3.7305536584451528`*^9, 
  3.7305536926049213`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f6df49c0-0396-4d62-8a55-\
0bb5e3cdebed"],

